# Design tooling

When the user asks about homemade design work — drawing assets, SVG paths, smoothing strokes, fills/strokes, layers, or exporting art for this project — assume they are using **Inkscape only**.

- Give Inkscape menu paths, shortcuts, and tool names (not Figma, Illustrator, etc.) unless they explicitly ask for another app.
- Export guidance should target SVG copied into `components/` (e.g. `VineDecoration.tsx`), with `viewBox` and path `d` attributes in mind.
